I"j<h1 id="entrypoint">ENTRYPOINT</h1>
<blockquote>
  <p>Defines the executable invoked when the container is started</p>

</blockquote>

<h1 id="cmd">CMD</h1>
<blockquote>
  <p>specifies the argument that get passed to the <code class="highlighter-rouge">ENTRYPOINT</code></p>

</blockquote>

<p>Although you can use the <code class="highlighter-rouge">CMD</code> instruction to specify the command you want to execute when the image is run,
the correct way is to do it though the <code class="highlighter-rouge">ENTRYPOINT</code> instruction and to only specify the CMD if you want to define the default arguments.</p>
